page.title: 07Ecology of Dornaford Farm
page.content: Our farm is mainly pasture,woodland and moor.I did this survey in May.These are the wild flowers that I found.Bluebells,violets,daisies,lesser celandine,red campion, white campion, stitch wort,herb robert,dandelion, shepherds purse,white deadnettle, ramson,primrose,dogs mercury,vetch, lady smock,purple spotted orchid, buttercup,wild garlic,ground ivy,pink percline,wood anemone,wood sorrel, gorse,wall pennywort,forgetmenot,green hellebore,ground nut,hawksbit,bugle, field speedwell,hairy buttercress, broom,goosegrass,wild strawberries, lords and ladies,rush grass,charlock, welsh poppy,greater celandine,stinging nettle,clover,tormentil,dogdaisy,dog violet. My Grandmother helped me to check the names of these flowers:by Catherine Walker.
